Title: Requires certain professionals to provide and the state education department to collect information about the practice of their professions; repealer
Summary: Requires certain professionals to provide and the state education department to collect information about the practice of their professions.
ActClause: AN ACT to amend the education law, in relation to requiring certain professionals to provide and the state education department to collect information about the practice of their professions; and repealing certain provisions of such law relating thereto
